<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَلَهُ شُرُوطٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أَحَدُهَا:</span> تَعْيِينُ الزَّوْجَيْنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَإِنْ أَشَارَ الوَلِيُّ إِلَى الزَّوْجَةِ، أَوْ سَمَّاهَا، أَوْ وَصَفَهَا بِمَا تَتَمَيَّزُ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ قَالَ:</span> زَوَّجْتُكَ بِنْتِي،<span class="c5"> وَلَهُ وَاحِدَةٌ لَا أَكْثَرَ:</span> صَحَّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
